嘅起伏<br />\n去諗一諗我 其實我都可以處理一個咁複雜嘅演唱會<br />\n無野你做唔到嘅<br />\n<br />\n人與人之間真係好特別<br />\n今日你哋可以坐到係到睇我表演或者我可以表演比你哋睇都係一個緣份"},{"pid":"1b65c2b47a5e77225d2c3b1172994d1e78e9ee02","tid":1502490,"uid":43966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:49:42.000Z","msg":"完未<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d213d17dd86fc00b2e723c94a2a84c388095b76","tid":1502490,"uid":302980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b65c2b47a5e77225d2c3b1172994d1e78e9ee02","tid":1502490,"uid":43966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:49:42.000Z","msg":"完未<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:51:03.000Z","msg":"0038完"},{"pid":"08f598d8257c741f1866045cdc4d7999e5014242","tid":1502490,"uid":172762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:51:32.000Z","msg":"好大風大雨 絲巴回家安全小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92c1274872acb404c88c407aa250719dccd02802","tid":1502490,"uid":209554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:56:40.000Z","msg":"屌，咁撚大雨"},{"pid":"debf0456271556e0a7ca3dd55edf89eaff1938ad","tid":1502490,"uid":254192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:59:47.000Z","msg":"冇雙冠軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f12bb9153806fc98ddf0b18bf13bd954ab27e042","tid":1502490,"uid":302980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"debf0456271556e0a7ca3dd55edf89eaff1938ad","tid":1502490,"uid":254192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:59:47.000Z","msg":"冇雙冠軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" cl